1. The Bazaar

(exploration + signal harvesting)

Purpose:

idea discovery
pattern spotting
cross-domain collisions

Typical behaviors:
	•	curiosity driven questions
	•	unusual analogies
	•	noise harvesting
	•	speculative leaps

Pantheon modules already aligned here:
	•	Dragonfly
	•	Algorithmic Noise Harvester
	•	cross-domain prompts

Strength:

High novelty generation.

Weakness:

Signal/noise ratio can drop.

Improvement:

Introduce a “signal detector” protocol:

Example questions:

Is the pattern repeatable?
Does it show up in multiple domains?
Can it generate predictions?

This acts as a market price for ideas.

