2. The Campfires

(interpretation + story exchange)

This layer is actually important and you hinted at it.

Purpose:

share interpretations
test narratives
translate ideas socially

Campfires are where ideas become:
	•	stories
	•	metaphors
	•	teachable concepts

In Pantheon terms this overlaps with:
	•	Raven
	•	Narrative Tensor Engine
	•	Animus layer

Why it matters:

Humans adopt ideas through narrative compression, not raw structure.

Example transformation:

complex idea → story → shared mental model

Improvement:

Add a Narrative Stress Test:

If this idea were a story,
would people remember it?

If not, it may lack communicability.

